{"type":null,"faqId":32874,"title":"【EMUI3.1及以上】拍照-心情水印","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:#333333;}\n.s2{color:#444444;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;color:red;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">走过很多地方，经过很多过往，用水印来铭记那些照片背后的阴霾或晴朗。</span><a href=\"http://cn.club.vmall.com/forum.php?gid=327%22 \\t %22_blank\"><span class=\"s2\">EMUI</span></a><span class=\"s1\">3.1相机之</span><span class=\"s3\">心情水印</span><span class=\"s1\">，多重方式来标记不同画面，定格每一个特别瞬间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>给照片添加水印就是赋予照片特别的意义。不同的水印标记的是不同心情，就如同日记一样，记录每一刻不同的地点或时间，还有甜蜜的心情或诗意的远方。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>看似寻常的水印，却有非同寻常的照片故事。身在远方，或心在路上，都需要一种形式来特别备注，希望EMUI3.1相机中优化后的水印功能给你更多合适搭配，满足你照片中的所有美好。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7594","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748435000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":21,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"拍照,心情水印","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}